Both subsequently resigned. Inzunza was sentenced to <a3_0><b8_0>21 months<b8_0/><a3_0/> in prison. In <a2_0><b7_0>2009<b7_0/><a2_0/>, a judge acquitted Zucchet on seven out of the nine counts against him, and granted his petition for a new trial on the other two charges; the remaining charges were eventually dropped.
